wiki.text:
'Keshet' (, Rainbow) may refer to:

In 'Television': *Keshet (TV) is one of the two concessionaires running the
Israeli commercial television Channel 2.

'Other uses': *Keshet (organization) is a social justice organization in Boston,
Massachusetts. *Keshet, Golan Heights is an Israeli moshav/settlement in the
Golan Heights.
